canonical:
  title: 寄息影菴禪老
  author: 李嵓
  language: lzh
  text: 浮世虛名是政丞小窓閑味卽山僧箇中亦有風流處一朶梅花照佛燈
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 寄息影菴禪老
  author: 李嵓
  language: lzh
  text: 浮世虛名是政丞。小窓閑味卽山僧。箇中亦有風流處。一朶梅花照佛燈。
korean:
  title: 기식영암선로
  author: 이암
  language: kor
  text: |-
    뜬 세상 헛이름은 바로 정승이요
    작은 창의 한가한 맛은 그저 산승일세
    그 중에도 또한 풍류로운 곳이 있나니
    한 송이 매화꽃이 부처등에 비치었네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_0170&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: A Letter to the Venerable Hermit of Repose Shadow Hermitage
  author: Lee Am
  language: eng
  text: |-
    In this fleeting world, empty fame belongs to the prime minister,
    While the quiet taste of a small window is the mountain monk's alone.
    Yet within this humble dwelling, there is elegance too—
    A single plum blossom reflected in the Buddha's lamp.
  footnotes:
    - '息影 (repose shadow): A classical allusion to withdrawal from public life and worldly affairs'
    - The poem contrasts the illusory glitter of high political office with the genuine spiritual refinement found in monastic simplicity
